    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1891-03-23T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1891-03-23T00:00:00-05:00" n="103"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d103">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Egan</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-03-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 23, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 86.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I desire to apprise you, in connection with
                    previous correspondence, of the receipt of a letter from the Secretary of the
                    Navy, of the 19th instant, saying the United States steamship <hi rend="italic"
                        >Pensacola</hi> arrived at Valparaiso, in obedience to the orders of that
                    Department, on the 28th of February, and that the United States steamship <hi
                        rend="italic">Baltimore</hi> was about to depart from Montevideo for the
                    same destination. It is also proposed to dispatch the United States steamship
                        <hi rend="italic">San Francisco</hi> from San Francisco as soon as
                    instructions can be sent to her.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James G. Blaine</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
